---
title: One-Pan Pulled Pork Banh Mi with Cucumber, Pickled Carrots & Radishes
description: Tonight’s dinner features a favorite Vietnamese sandwich with a twist: pickled veggies are piled between toasty baguettes for a banh mi-inspired sammie, BBQ-style! Pulled pork is coated in tangy hoisin for a barbecue-like kick, then topped with cucumber, radishes, carrots, and a generous swipe of mayo. Top with a squeeze of lime juice, pile leftover veggies on the side, then prepare for total taste bud takeover.
